Title: Noncommutative Differential Geometry and Connections on Simplicial

ManifoldsComments: LaTeX2e, uses AMS-LaTeX package, 25 pages

Journal-ref: Acta Phys.Polon. B28 (1997) 1039-1070

For a simplicial manifold we construct the differential geometry structureand use it to investigate linear connections, metric and gravity. We discussand compare three main approaches and calculate the resulting gravity actionfunctionals.